abstract: >-
  ZenBrain is an open-source 7-layer memory system for AI agents,
  implementing neuroscience-inspired mechanisms: spaced repetition (FSRS),
  Hebbian learning with homeostatic normalization, Ebbinghaus forgetting
  curves, emotional memory tagging, sleep consolidation (replay
  simulation), Bayesian confidence propagation, and context-dependent
  retrieval. Pure TypeScript, zero runtime dependencies for the core
  algorithm package. v0.3.x adds 10 advanced algorithms grounded in
  recent neuroscience and ML research.
